Brief:

    - card creation success using dictionaryRoomDatabase and imageApi
    - database error: any DictionaryRepository Exception, - manual card creation feature applied
    - imageApi serverError: response.code() -> 500; 503
    - imageApi NoInternetConnectionException


Details:

    1) Card creation success using dictionaryRoomDatabase and imageApi

         a) Word selection from dropdown menu:
             - "ab" characters typing
             - dropdown menu has shown
             - select a word in a dropdown menu
             - wordAutoCompleteEditText shows selected word

         b) Select a translation:
             - click translationSpinner
             - click on the item in a dropdown menu
             - clicked item is in the translationSpinner

         c) Select an example pair(sentence - translation):
             - click exampleSpinner
             - click on the item in a dropdown menu
             - clicked item is in the exampleSpinner

         d) Select image:
             - click imageSpinner
             - click the image in a dropdown menu
             - selected image is in a collapsed imageSpinner

         e) Select a group title:
             - type group name characters
             - select a group name in a dropdown menu
             - check: wordAutoCompleteEditText shows selected word

         f) createButton click appends new card to cardGroupFragment
             - click create button
             - cardGroupFragment inflation
             - check a new CardView presence, containing selected items:
                    word, translation, example, image, group name;


    2) Database error: any DictionaryRepository Exception, - manual card creation feature applied

        - type a word in a wordAutoCompleteTextView,
        - show database error message:"database error, you may create a card manually (ok)"
        - click errorMessageOkButton
        - inflate manual_card_creation_layout
        - type a word in a wordTextView
        - click wordConfirmationOkButton
        - translationEditText's highlighted
        - type a translation, click translationOkButton
        - exampleEditText's highlighted
        - type an example, click exampleOkButton
        - imageSpinner's highlighted
        - click imageSpinner
        - select 0 position image in a dropdown menu
        - cardGroupTitleEditText's highlighted
        - type a card group title, click cardGroupTitleOkButton
        - click createCardButton
        - check: whether an inflated CardGroupFragment has a new CardView containing respective:
                  word, translation, example, image, group name;


    3) imageApi serverError: response.code() -> 500; 503

        - type a word in a wordAutoCompleteTextView
        - click imageSpinner
        - show a message: "image data source error: skip image selection (ok)"
        - click ok button
        - dismiss imageSpinner

    4) imageApi NoInternetConnectionException

        a) internet connection established finally
            - enable airplane mode
            - type a word in a wordAutoCompleteTextView
            - click imageSpinner
            - show a message: "no internet connection, please check it (network spinner)"
            - disable airplane mode
            - error message with spinner dismissed
            - click image spinner
            - select image
            - imageSpinner replaced with image

        b) no internet connection eventually

            - enable airplane mode
            - type a word in a wordAutoCompleteTextView
            - click imageSpinner
            - show a message: "no internet connection, please check it (network spinner)"
            - 10 seconds later show the message:
                "you may skip image selection for a while and append this one later (wait)|(ok)"
            - click ok
            - dismiss image spinner


